for the rest of your life?

662
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:08,640
Sen.

663
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:10,800
You're the best man

664
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,030
I've ever met.

665
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,550
If I can't marry you,

666
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:18,880
it'll be the biggest regret of my life.

667
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:24,880
When something happened a few days ago,

668
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,920
I truly thought I was going to die.

669
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,590
Thank you.

670
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,230
With me this whole time.

671
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:36,000
But that was something
I had to face alone,

672
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:37,470
