673
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,510
Well, maybe...

674
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,360
Well...

675
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,210
Well,

676
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:44,510
