677
00:37:44,510 --> 00:37:46,110
Go abroad, stay as long as we want.

678
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,920
Maybe after some time,
we'll feel better.

679
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,760
Sen.

680
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:53,960
