681
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,320
I'm sorry.

682
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:04,710
For making you wait so long.

683
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:09,030
I owe you so much.

684
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:11,880
Maybe

685
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:15,190
