to repay you.

686
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,510
Does it taste good?

687
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,200
Let's kiss.

688
00:38:57,660 --> 00:38:59,360
You want to kiss
without wiping your mouth.

689
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:03,710
Hey, Xiaoxi.

690
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,550
Hey.

691
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:07,670
Aren't you two…

692
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:09,070
Huh?

693
00:39:10,590 --> 00:39:11,430
