703
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:30,000
After I talked to you last time,

704
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,840
I realized I was wrong.

705
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:33,280
So...

706
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:37,030
