Thanks.

722
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,200
No problem.

723
00:40:14,800 --> 00:40:15,800
Xiaoxi.

724
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:17,880
I think

725
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:19,920
