726
00:40:21,090 --> 00:40:22,510
Love each other, then stay together.

727
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:23,760
Have a problem, then solve it.

728
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:26,230
If you really can't solve it,

729
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:27,630
