730
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,150
In the end,
we all have to live for ourselves.

731
00:40:32,510 --> 00:40:33,350
Yeah.

732
00:40:36,150 --> 00:40:37,440
How about you and Bei?

733
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:40,960
Same as before.

734
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:43,360
